text.tspan: PRISME TOP BOARD (INPUT BOARD) - Complete Schematic
Board: 90mm × 55mm custom-cut ElectroCookie protoboard | Position: Middle layer
------ CV INPUT PROTECTION (Rear Jack -> A4 ADC) ------
Purpose: Scale 0-5V input -> 0-2.62V safe for 3.3V ADC | BAT85 clamp protects from overvoltage
CV Activity LED (rear panel, 7mm right of jack):
------ TRIG INPUT PROTECTION (Rear Jack -> A3 ADC) ------
Purpose: Identical to CV input | Scale 0-5V input -> 0-2.62V safe for 3.3V ADC
TRIG Mode/Activity RGB LED (rear panel, 7mm right of jack):
• Voltage dividers (R14-R15, R16-R17) scale 5V -> 2.62V for safe ADC operation
• BAT85 Schottky diodes clamp overvoltage to 3.3V (protection from >5V inputs)
• Dual-stage RC filtering (100nF + 10nF) removes high-frequency noise and RF interference
• RGB LED: GREEN = V-Trig mode | RED = S-Trig mode | Activity = brightness
• All decoupling caps close to power pins: C11 (bulk), C12 (bypass)
